  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A TUI RSS reader that renders feed images <em class=\"\">inline</em> in the terminal — no browser, no separate image viewer — by implementing the Kitty Graphics Protocol in pure Rust. Part of the <a href=\"/tag/vulpes-nvim\" class=\"internal-link text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Vulpes Nvim</a> aesthetic, for reading the web without leaving the terminal.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The Kitty Graphics Protocol implementation in Rust — loading and streaming images straight into the terminal\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/vulpes-rss/code.png\" alt=\"The Kitty Graphics Protocol implementation in Rust — loading and streaming images straight into the terminal\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/vulpes-rss/code.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/vulpes-rss/code.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/vulpes-rss/code.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/vulpes-rss/code.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The Kitty Graphics Protocol implementation in Rust — loading and streaming images straight into the terminal\" width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.9deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1400×900\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The Kitty Graphics Protocol implementation in Rust — loading and streaming images straight into the terminal</figcaption>\n</figure>",
